---
// Testimonials.astro
---

<section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <span
                class="text-orange-500 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm"
                >Client Experiences</span
            >
            <h2
                class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mt-2 mb-4"
            >
                Loved by Homeowners
            </h2>
            <div
                class="w-24 h-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-orange-600 mx-auto rounded-full"
            >
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Review 1 -->
            <div
                class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col justify-between"
            >
                <div>
                    <div class="flex text-yellow-500 mb-4">
                        {
                            [...Array(5)].map(() => (
                                <svg
                                    class="w-5 h-5"
                                    fill="currentColor"
                                    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                                >
                                    <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
                                </svg>
                            ))
                        }
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 italic mb-6">
                        "Roy at Rittenworx was fantastic! He repaired the
                        drywall from some old water damage and matched the
                        texture perfectly. He showed up when he said he would,
                        completely cleaned up after himself, and stuck exactly
                        to his original quote. Hard to find reliable contractors
                        in Madison, but this one is a keeper."
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-gray-100 pt-4 mt-auto"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-700 font-bold"
                    >
                        SM
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight">
                            Sarah M.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Madison, AL</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Review 2 -->
            <div
                class="bg-blue-900 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl transform md:-translate-y-4 flex flex-col justify-between relative"
            >
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 text-white">
                    <svg
                        class="w-16 h-16"
                        fill="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        ><path
                            d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"
                        ></path></svg
                    >
                </div>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="flex text-orange-400 mb-4">
                        {
                            [...Array(5)].map(() => (
                                <svg
                                    class="w-5 h-5"
                                    fill="currentColor"
                                    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                                >
                                    <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
                                </svg>
                            ))
                        }
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-white italic mb-6">
                        "I had a huge list of 'honey do' items that I just
                        didn't have time for: ceiling fan installation, fixing a
                        squeaky door, and replacing some trim. Rittenworx
                        tackled the whole list in one day. The carpentry work
                        was especially impressive. Highly recommend for any home
                        repairs!"
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-blue-800 pt-4 mt-auto"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-800 flex items-center justify-center text-orange-400 font-bold"
                    >
                        DR
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-bold text-white leading-tight">
                            David R.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-blue-300">Huntsville, AL</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Review 3 -->
            <div
                class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col justify-between"
            >
                <div>
                    <div class="flex text-yellow-500 mb-4">
                        {
                            [...Array(5)].map(() => (
                                <svg
                                    class="w-5 h-5"
                                    fill="currentColor"
                                    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                                >
                                    <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
                                </svg>
                            ))
                        }
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 italic mb-6">
                        "They installed LVP flooring in our entire downstairs
                        and completely repainted our living room. It looks
                        incredible. Professional, fast, and exactly what we
                        wanted. It's so nice having a local company you know is
                        fully licensed and insured doing the heavy lifting."
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-gray-100 pt-4 mt-auto"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-orange-100 flex items-center justify-center text-orange-700 font-bold"
                    >
                        JL
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight">
                            Jessica L.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Decatur, AL</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
